name: MetaInside by Virtuals
description: MetaInside is a cutting-edge multi-AI agent platform for seamless DApp development, catering to both beginners and experienced developers. It offers no-code AI-assisted creation and direct coding options. Powered by open-source LLMs like Deepseek R1, it runs on a MIN token-driven ecosystem. Built by GenesisLab.com, MetaInside ensures flexibility, security, and innovation in blockchain development.
